      <title>高通赞助曼联，加大个人电脑业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-01/qualcomm-sponsors-manchester-united-amid-bigger-pc-push-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高通已成为曼联足球俱乐部的新球衣赞助商，此举旨在提高其骁龙品牌在消费者中的知名度，同时推动个人计算的发展。彭博社的 Ian King 与 Ed Ludlow 一起在“彭博科技”上讨论并展示了这一新合作关系。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-01/qualcomm-sponsors-manchester-united-amid-bigger-pc-push-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 20:32:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
