      <title>拉加德称欧洲央行需要时间评估不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-01/lagarde-ecb-needs-time-to-assess-inflation-uncertainties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，欧洲央行有时间评估即将公布的信息，因为欧元区就业市场依然强劲。她在葡萄牙辛特拉主持欧洲央行年度央行论坛开幕式时发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-01/lagarde-ecb-needs-time-to-assess-inflation-uncertainties</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 20:16:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
